I am planning to try this recipe tonight, so I'm not exactly reviewing it -- just responding to John Kumler who asked about the skewers and not singeing them. I soak bamboo or wood skewers for an hour in cold water, then thread the meat and/or veggies on. This keeps them from burning on the grill.

